Park Place Boat & RV Storage
At Park Place Boat & RV, we believe in accessible, affordable, and secure storage solutions with a personalized approach.
Our History
A vision in the making, longtime friends and business owners, with a combined 100 years of experience, have joined forces to bring Zephyrhills a state of the art boat and rv storage facility.  We believe in offering various storage options, with competitive pricing, and peace of mind knowing that your assets will be protected with our high tech monitoring system.
